Time - Interface in net.varkhan.base.management.metric
A time source.

The Time.time() method provide a measure of elapsed time, for some arbitrary notion of time and since some arbitrary origin.

Timer - Interface in net.varkhan.base.management.metric
A time elapsed source.

This interface expands the contract provided by Time by providing ways to reset the origin of time to a specific instant (so that the value of time at that instant is 0) and stop and start the increase of time (so that the value of time at the instant of start is the same as its value at the last stop or reset).
